snippet.title: LAURE X EKDEV LIMBU - TIHAR SONG [OFFICIAL VIDEO 2025] | KABITA NEPALI
snippet.description:
Actually, I created this song long time ago but whenever I listen to it, I felt something incomplete and I thought that I could do lot of experiments to make this song more close towards the perfection. This year, finally, with the help, courage and push from my beloved people I am able to present you guys this beautiful masterpiece. 

‚ÄúTIHAR SONG‚Äù is an occasional song but if you dissect this creation musically and visually, you can find lots of interesting things, which will make your normal days; lightened and brighten up like Tihar. Happy Tihar to you all. May goddess Laxmi bless you and your family with wealth and good health. Jay Nepal üá≥üáµ

Stream it here:- https://song.link/tiharsong

Today, the SMASH RULE takes over:

üß® What is the SMASH RULE?

1Ô∏è‚É£ At the end of Day 2, the overall leader‚Äôs total points +10 will become the Match Point threshold.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Today is the day! Once a team reaches or exceeds the Match Point threshold, they must win a Chicken Dinner in a subsequent match to be crowned champions
3Ô∏è‚É£ Be the Champions! ‚Äì If no team meets both conditions by the end of all 18 matches, the team with the highest total points will be declared the champion.

Everything is on the line ‚ÄîTrophy, legacy, and one final zone.

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm. A person who recites this Aarti with true devotion is blessed with wealth and prosperity and a good family life. The worship of Laxmi and the regular chanting of the chalisa is recommended, to those wishing to free their Karma of all the past misdeeds.

The biggest, spiciest ad film of the year is HERE! 
Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Watch the explosive trailer of AGENT CHING ATTACKS with jaw-dropping action, whistle-worthy drama, foot-tapping music, and masala so hot‚Ä¶ it‚Äôll set your screen on fire.

The full film premieres Sunday, October 19 exclusively on this channel.

WHAT TO EXPECT:
‚Ä¢ Ranveer Singh in his most powerful avatar yet as Agent Ching
‚Ä¢ Sreeleela adding spice and swagger as Agent Mirchi
‚Ä¢ Bobby Deol unleashing chaos as Professor White Noise
‚Ä¢ Signature Atlee scale, style & spectacle with a global A-list crew
‚Ä¢ A brand-new version of the iconic anthem ‚ÄúMy Name is Ranveer Ching‚Äù

From Bhatinda to Beijing, there‚Äôs only one king‚Ä¶ Ranveer Ching!

This is the BIGGEST celebration of Desi Chinese ever ‚Äî bold, flavourful, cinematic, and guaranteed to #AagLagaDe.

About Ching‚Äôs Secret - They say that to win Hindustani hearts even Chinese food became desi! And there‚Äôs only one Desi Chinese food brand that can make desi hearts beat faster ‚Äì Ching‚Äôs. Saucy. Spicy. Sweet and sour. Hot and sour. Crunchy. Slurpy. Zesty. Schezwani. Manchurian‚Ä¶ Whatever be the kind of Desi Chinese your palate craves for, only Ching‚Äôs can hit the spot with a perfect zing.

id.description:
Film iklan terbesar dan terpedas tahun ini telah HADIR!
Atlee x Ranveer Singh berkolaborasi dengan Sreeleela & Bobby Deol untuk ledakan sinematik terliar yang memadukan aksi, drama, komedi, & masala.

Tonton trailer AGENT CHING ATTACKS yang eksplosif dengan aksi yang memukau, drama yang memukau, musik yang menghentak, dan masala yang begitu panas... akan membakar semangat Anda.

Film lengkapnya tayang perdana Minggu, 19 Oktober, eksklusif di kanal ini.

APA YANG HARUS DIHARAPKAN:
‚Ä¢ Ranveer Singh dalam avatar terkuatnya sebagai Agen Ching
‚Ä¢ Sreeleela menambahkan bumbu dan gaya sebagai Agen Mirchi
‚Ä¢ Bobby Deol melepaskan kekacauan sebagai Profesor White Noise
‚Ä¢ Skala, gaya, & tontonan khas Atlee dengan kru papan atas dunia
‚Ä¢ Versi baru dari lagu kebangsaan ikonik "My Name is Ranveer Ching"

Dari Bhatinda hingga Beijing, hanya ada satu raja‚Ä¶ Ranveer Ching!

Ini adalah perayaan TERBESAR untuk orang Tionghoa Desi ‚Äî berani, penuh cita rasa, sinematik, dan dijamin #AagLagaDe.

Tentang Rahasia Ching - Konon untuk memenangkan hati orang Hindustan, bahkan makanan Tionghoa pun menjadi desi! Dan hanya ada satu merek makanan Tionghoa Desi yang dapat membuat hati orang desi berdebar lebih kencang ‚Äì Ching's. Berkuah. Pedas. Manis asam. Panas asam. Renyah. Slurpy. Segar. Schezwani. Manchuria‚Ä¶ Apa pun jenis masakan Tionghoa Desi yang Anda idamkan, hanya Ching yang bisa memuaskan selera Anda dengan rasa yang sempurna.

Saya ‚ô• Tionghoa Desi!

De grootste en meest pittige reclamefilm van het jaar is HIER!

Atlee x Ranveer Singh bundelen hun krachten met Sreeleela en Bobby Deol voor de wildste filmische explosie van actie, drama, komedie en masala.

Bekijk de explosieve trailer van AGENT CHING ATTACKS met adembenemende actie, fluitend drama, swingende muziek en masala zo heet... dat je scherm ervan in vuur en vlam staat.

De volledige film gaat op zondag 19 oktober exclusief op dit kanaal in premi√®re.

WAT JE KUNT VERWACHTEN:
‚Ä¢ Ranveer Singh in zijn krachtigste avatar tot nu toe als Agent Ching
‚Ä¢ Sreeleela voegt pit en bravoure toe als Agent Mirchi
‚Ä¢ Bobby Deol ontketent chaos als Professor White Noise
‚Ä¢ De kenmerkende Atlee-schaal, stijl en spektakel met een wereldwijde A-lijst crew
‚Ä¢ Een gloednieuwe versie van het iconische volkslied "My Name is Ranveer Ching"

Van Bhatinda tot Beijing, er is maar √©√©n koning... Ranveer Ching!

Dit is het GROOTSTE feest van Desi Chinees ooit ‚Äî gedurfd, smaakvol, filmisch en gegarandeerd #AagLagaDe.

Over Ching's Secret - Ze zeggen dat zelfs Chinees eten desi werd om Hindoestaanse harten te veroveren! En er is maar √©√©n Desi Chinees merk dat desi harten sneller kan laten kloppen: Ching's. Pittig. Pittig. Zoetzuur. Pittig. Knapperig. Slurpend. Pittig. Manchurian... Wat voor soort Desi Chinees je smaakpapillen ook verlangen, alleen Ching's kan perfect smaken.

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic - Official Trailer #2 (2025)
snippet.description:
Watch the new Baahubali: The Epic trailer for this upcoming film starring Prabhas, Rana Daggubati, Anushka Shetty, Tamannaah Bhatia, Sathyaraj, Ramya Krishnan, and Nassar.

Sivudu is an orphan who is rescued from a river as a baby and raised in a quiet tribal village at the foot of a towering waterfall. His world remains limited until a mysterious warrior‚Äôs mask falls from above, awakening a deep curiosity. Determined to discover its origin, he climbs the waterfall and uncovers a kingdom caught in the grip of tyranny and rebellion.

There he meets Avantika, a rebel fighting to rescue Devasena, a princess who has been wrongfully imprisoned for twenty-five years. Inspired by Avantika‚Äôs courage and driven by love, Sivudu joins the mission. When he enters Mahishmati and frees Devasena, the people begin to recognise him. During a confrontation, the royal guard Kattappa stops the fight and kneels before Sivudu, revealing that he is Mahendra Baahubali, the son of the noble prince Amarendra Baahubali.

The past unravels: Amarendra and his cousin Bhallaladeva were raised as heirs by the matriarch Sivagami. Though Amarendra was crowned king for his wisdom and compassion, Bhallaladeva‚Äôs jealousy led to betrayal. Manipulated by lies, Sivagami ordered Amarendra‚Äôs death, carried out by a loyal but misled Kattappa.

Now, Mahendra must rise. With Kattappa and the rebels beside him, he challenges Bhallaladeva, rescues Devasena, and reclaims the throne of Mahishmati.

10 years before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen.

Baahubali: The Epic, directed and written by SS Rajamouli, opens in theaters worldwide on October 31, 2025.

#phobia #analoghorror #creepy
#minecrafthorror #analoghorror #phobia  

I Survived SCARIEST TAX MAN in Minecraft
In this video, me and my friend face the SCARIEST TAX MAN ever seen in Minecraft! What started as a normal day quickly turned into a nightmare when this horrifying creature began hunting us down, demanding something far more terrifying than diamonds. We tried to hide, build, and fight back ‚Äî but nothing could stop him. Will we survive his deadly collection spree or lose everything? Watch till the end to find out!

snippet.title: Ujan Shakya - Baby (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
MEY STUDIO & VISIONS MEDIA PRODUCTION
PRESENTS

BABY by Ujan Shakya || New Newari Song || New Nepal Bhasa Song || New Nepali Song

"Baby" explores the theme of love. It depicts the concept of love at first sight through a narrative that combines imagination and emotion. The piece is characterized as an emotional afrobeat , featuring a blend of Newari instruments.

Mera naam hai emiway bantai 
Flow aj bhi juna vidyalay

Khauf bhi ha apne se khauf khata yaha pe toh 
Tere ilaake ko banadu mirzapur 
Flow inke out dated hai 
Ab likhta paper mei 
Patent hai mere pages toh 
Mujhe pay kare 
Playful hai wordplay pehle se 
Hum play kare 
Peth bharre mujhse leke beef 
Lekin pray karre 

Front cover pe nai aate bantai kya hai scene 
Ye paisa deke khabar mei 
Hum cover mei 
Bas khali karna janta mei magazine 
Book mei aur pen mera pistol hai 
Industry ka khel beta janega toh sab jhol
Hai band hole hai jabse mei aaya saare 
Rat fase pade 
Bane champ pehla rank leke khade 
Kare trap toh fir bag nai hum bank leke 
Khade chal 


(Hook)

Mera naam hai 
Bolna nai padta hai 
Ab mera kaam bolta hai 
Mera naam hai 
Naam aisa har koi hum ko 
Salaam thokta hai 
Mera naam hai 
Naam hai tabhi toh hum badnaam hai 
Chote 
Mera naam hai 
Haha malum hai na 

(Verse)

My bars got the barcode 
They‚Äôll lead you to narcos 
Lines so dope got confused for cargos 
Look at these bitches calling me clown 
I‚Äôm pennywise with the pen drag kids itno dark holes 

Don‚Äôt ever f#ckin rap in english again, bi#ch.
Did your pu##y a## really trademark this language 
Bars soo savage i cut bandwidth for online 
Gangsters cyber damage 

I‚Äôm shredding the charts 
Heavy disaster for you su#kers
Steady with bars get ready for scars pen like a blade 
Tearing apart weapon in charge
Dropping these bombs 
Call me kim jong 
I‚Äôm lunatic armed 

You‚Äôre a frog in the pond 
I‚Äôm in the sea with the sharks 
Turning kings into pawns 
Selling combs to the bald 
Ek hi flow mei tu tatata
Lou#e ka baal karke bhi na 
Hota famous na liya hota ye naam 

(Hook)

Bhai tera tufaan hai 
Aisa ye zubaan hai 
Summe sunta mujhe 
Bachkane tu fan hai 
Kyu panic hora be mujhjaisa 
Tu na hai 
Juna hai rhyme sceme logo ko
Lagara chuna hai hai 
Aae panwadi 
Mere bina scene pura suna hai 
Sunnata 
Yaha par hi banna tha 
Wyapari nai mujhe rapper hi 
Banna tha upar toh waise bhi 
Moksh hai ye baatein parlok se 
Expect kya karu par log se 
Kick karre day one se hustler hum 
Kok se 
Slow jara flow toh le force mei 

Opponent ko deta nai opportunity 
Brutally maru usse mei usually 
Har bari teri kyu jali 
Casually reppin globally 
Jab bola ye tu roo padi 
Mere bina tu nobody 
Dhua dia mei sober hi 
Ab aayi teri woh ghadi 
Bars du lage hathkadi 
Baaz nai aane wala mei 
Baaz bana hu upar hi 
Fast mei jab ye flow chali 
Saas na lu ye new delhi 
Pranaam kar hum too pak 
Iss naam se tu chalpadi

snippet.title: I Got Hunted By Minecraft's Smartest Player
snippet.description:
help me bro i'm scared

I Got Hunted By Minecraft's Smartest Player

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner Swap VS 2 Hunters
snippet.description:
This was crazy intense. Manhunt, but with a twist.

This video, I teamed up with a Manhunt NOOB, Dr Donut, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dreampublic


In this challenge Dr Donut and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.

This is one of my first ever collabs of this type, if you'd like to see more, like the video!

This was played on Minecraft 1.21.8, and is a custom coded challenge. There were a few bugs that we plan to iron out before we try something like this again!

200,000 likes for me to try this challenge with someone else!


DrDonut: @DrDonutt 
Skeppy: @Skeppy 
Daquavis: @DaquavisMC 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken
